Forward + Inverse Mode:

COMMANDS:

     h,help      Display this message.
     b,back      Return to main menu.
     df          Print a list of the driving functions that may be used for the forward and inverse algorithms.

INSTRUCTIONS:

    1. Enter the indices of the driving functions that you wish to run seperated by a space (e.g. 0 2 8)
    2. Enter the following arguments for the run paramters:
        [start time] [end time] [outer resolution] [inner resolution] [save plot] [save data] [rest] [all]
    3. That's it.
